l made this herd, so you need
to start treating me with some respect.

34
00:05:57,712 --> 00:06:01,132
- Come on, Sid.
- Sid, we were just kidding.

35
00:06:01,132 --> 00:06:05,761
- Hey, let's play pin-the-tail-on-the-mammoth.
- Yeah!

36
